310
00:16:59,393 --> 00:17:00,311
Obrigado.

311
00:17:01,395 --> 00:17:02,980
Você é família, Michael.

312
00:17:03,564 --> 00:17:04,732
Trabalhe onde for.

313
00:17:10,154 --> 00:17:11,322
Sra. Gunnerson.

314
00:17:13,282 --> 00:17:14,283
